creative_name = "Confidence starts inside elevate with men inner vests"
creative_df = df[df['creative_name'] == creative_name]

if creative_df.empty:
    result = f"Creative '{creative_name}' not found in the data."
else:
    total_spend = creative_df['spend'].sum()
    total_impressions = creative_df['impressions'].sum()
    total_clicks = creative_df['clicks'].sum()
    total_purchases = creative_df['purchases'].sum()
    total_revenue = creative_df['revenue'].sum()

    ctr = (total_clicks / total_impressions) if total_impressions > 0 else 0
    roas = (total_revenue / total_spend) if total_spend > 0 else 0

    result = {
        "creative_name": creative_name,
        "total_spend": total_spend,
        "total_impressions": total_impressions,
        "total_clicks": total_clicks,
        "ctr": ctr,
        "total_purchases": total_purchases,
        "total_revenue": total_revenue,
        "roas": roas
    }
